{
  "texts": [
    "This research presents a conceptual debate on the integration of generative AI in organizations to strengthen the internal organizational knowledge management system.",
    "The study has adopted a case study to strengthen the conceptual debate for the integrated model, which has provided evidence from the experience of professionals working in diverse fields and positions.",
    "It is still imperative to investigate and explore the phenomenon through practical dimensions.",
    "For that, future researchers may explore the feasibility of our model in an actual work environment using quantitative and experimental research design.",
    "Extensive development in artificial intelligence and generative AI made them stand alone with no alternatives and competition; however, being an evolving concept in organizational research and practice, it urges extensive research focus (Burger et al., 2023)."
  ]
}